    <p>Before U<sub>f</sub>, the upper register is in the state H<sup>⊗n</sup>|0⟩ with N = 2<sup>n</sup>. How many basis states are in this superposition, and what is the amplitude of each?</p>
  </div>
  <div class="answer-area">
    <div class="answer-row">
