  <div style="font-family:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;font-size:0.72rem;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:0.6rem;">Interactive: trace Shor's algorithm step by step</div>
  <div style="display:flex;gap:0.5rem;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;margin-bottom:0.6rem;">
