<!-- Exercise 8.1 -->
<div class="ex-block">
  <div class="ex-header"><span class="ex-tag">Ex 8.1</span><span class="ex-title">How many qubits are needed?</span></div>
  <div class="ex-body">
    <p>To factor n = 15 with N = 1024 = 2¹⁰, how many qubits are in the upper register? And how many bits are needed for the lower register (to store values 0–15)?</p>
  </div>
